sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant R as Argo Rollouts
  participant I as Ingress
  participant C as Canary Pods
  participant O as Observability/Metric Provider

  R->>I: set canary weight (5%)
  R->>O: run analysis step
  O-->>R: error_rate=0.01, p95=120ms
  alt within thresholds
    R->>I: increase weight (20%)
  else exceeds thresholds
    R->>I: set weight 0% (abort)
    R->>R: rollback to stable
  end
